In re Resignation of Carter.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Carter (1988), 39 Ohio St. 3d 606.]

(No. D.R. 88-7 — Submitted October 19, 1988 — Decided November 23, 1988.)

The resignation of Robert A. Carter, Jr. as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
